sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant A as External Agent
    participant SSE as /mcp SSE
    participant MW as ProjectTokenMiddleware
    participant M as MCP Tool Handler
    participant C as Query Cache
    participant R as GraphRegistry
    participant G as FalkorDB Graph
    participant T as Trace Recorder
    participant S as CG-first Strategy

    A->>S: Ask for repository context
    S->>SSE: Open MCP session
    SSE->>MW: Validate bearer token

    alt Token invalid
        MW-->>A: 401 or 403
    else Token valid
        MW->>M: Route tool call in project context
        M->>C: Check cached retrieval
        alt Cache hit
            C-->>M: Cached result
        else Cache miss
            M->>R: Resolve current project graph
            R->>G: Query symbols and relationships
            G-->>M: Graph result
            M->>C: Store result in cache
        end
        M->>T: Record tool call, latency, result
        M-->>S: Graph-backed context
        S->>S: Score context quality under token budget
        alt Graph quality sufficient
            S-->>A: Return ContextGraph evidence
        else Quality too low
            S->>S: Read bounded local snippets as fallback
            S-->>A: Return graph evidence plus local snippets
        end
    end